LaTeX Configuration I prefer to configure formular delimiters with the way using brackets:
inline: \(...\) display: \[...\] display + equation number: \[...\] (1) For vscode, install extension Markdown+Math, then change Configuration from dollars into brackets. For mathJax, it&rsquo;s provided in the default configuration.
Good memory is not as bad as a pen.
Permutation A_n^n=n\times(n-1)\times(n-2)\times...\times2\times1
A_n^m=n\times(n-1)\times(n-2)\times...\times(n-m+1) = \frac{n!}{(n-m)!}
Combination C_n^m=\frac{A_n^m}{A_m^m} = \frac{n!}{m!(n-m)!}
C_n^m=C_n^{n-m} C_{n+1}^{r+1} = C_n^r + C_n^{r+1}
Binomial theorem (a+b)^n = \sum_{i=0}^n{{C_n^i}a^{n-i}b^i} \tag 1 2^n =\sum_{i=0}^n{{C_n^i}} = C_n^0 + C_n^1 + C_n^2 + .
